data.description: Welcome to this charming and cozy 3 bedroom 1.5 bath colonial located in the beautiful city of Olmsted Falls. This home is situated on a large, wooded lot, with a deck, patio and fire pit providing you with ample space to relax and enjoy nature. The two-story garage offers plenty of storage space, and the first-floor laundry room adds convenience to your daily routine. Step inside and be impressed by the warm and inviting atmosphere of this home. The well-appointed kitchen boasts plenty of counter space, a walk in pantry, newer appliances and a vaulted ceiling. The spacious dining room and living room is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining friends. Upstairs you will find two of the three bedrooms, each with its own unique charm. The home has been updated with a  new complete tear off roof in 2020, water heater 2021, updated windows, bathtub update 2023 and a freshly painted kitchen and dining room. This adorable home is located just a stone's throw away from the charming downtown of Olmsted Falls, offering a variety of restaurants, shops, and entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely house your home today!
